OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,FJournalist Humam Husari spent years
OL,7,Fdocumenting the reality of life during
OL,8,FSyria's civil war for ITV News and was
OL,9,Ffinally reunited with his family in
OL,10,F2018
OL,12,FWith only a small camera and a laptop,
OL,13,FHumam Husari spent years documenting
OL,14,Flives of ordinary people during the
OL,15,FSyrian civil war for ITV News.
OL,17,FNow, after 50 years of Assad family
OL,18,Frule, Humam shared his joy that the
OL,19,Fregime has fallen.
