OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,F"It is a happy day in Syria, the
OL,7,Fhappiest. We're not afraid anymore of
OL,8,Fanything," Humam said, "It's a
OL,9,Fwonderful feeling. It's the best, one
OL,10,Fof the best."
OL,12,FAs a young filmmaker, Humam bore
OL,13,Fwitness to the brutal Assad regime
OL,14,Ffrom a small rebel-controlled corner
OL,15,Fof Damascus, and helped to highlight
OL,16,Fthe suffering of the Syrian people.
OL,18,FDue to his work filming the protests
OL,19,Fin 2011, Humam was forced to flee with
OL,20,Fhis wife, as Assad's forces came
OL,21,Flooking for him.
