OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,FITV News followed Humam as he was
OL,7,Freunited with his parents in Turkey,
OL,8,Fwho he had not seen for five years
OL,10,FBut he later secretly returned to
OL,11,FDamascus, to the suburb of Ghouta,
OL,12,Fafter feeling a sense of duty to
OL,13,Freturn to his home country.
OL,15,F"I couldn't just live my life normally
OL,16,Fknowing that people are living under
OL,17,Fbombing," he said. "I thought,
OL,18,Fsomething must be done, just to let
OL,19,Fthe world know what's going on."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
