OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,FIt was near where he was staying in
OL,7,FGhouta that Humam was first able to
OL,8,Fconfirm the use of chemical weapons by
OL,9,FSyrian government forces on its own
OL,10,Fcivilians to ITV News.
OL,12,F"I think somehow the camera creates
OL,13,Fsome kind of a shield between you and
OL,14,Fwhat you are trying to feel. And I
OL,15,Fthink the adrenaline in your body just
OL,16,Ftries to protect you," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
