OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,F"When I look back at my footage, I
OL,7,Fjust don't believe that I was there.
OL,8,FIt's just a lot of bodies trying to
OL,9,Fbreathe. You just don't know how to
OL,10,Fhelp them."
OL,12,F"To do such thing just to remain in
OL,13,Fpower, I think it's unbelievable," he
OL,14,Fadded, referencing the Assad regime.
OL,16,FUsing Humam's footage, ITV News made
OL,17,Fdozens of reports on the Syrian war
OL,18,Fover the last 13 years. But the
OL,19,Fconsequences of documenting the war
OL,20,Fhave not been easy for him or his
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
