OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,FDuring the regime, Humam's sister,
OL,7,FHaber, was jailed for nine months,
OL,8,Fpaying a heavy price for his
OL,9,Fjournalism.
OL,11,FHumam was able to reconnect with Haber
OL,12,Fin the last two days, and was also
OL,13,Fable to reach other members of his
OL,14,Ffamily in Damascus for the first time
OL,15,Fin months.
OL,17,F"She said: I'm happy that they didn't
OL,18,Fget to you," Humam said, "we can now
OL,19,Fplan to live together again in Syria
OL,20,Fand to build our country again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
