OL,3,CSyrian filmmaker shares his hopes and
OL,4,Cfears for country as Assad regime falls
OL,6,FOver the years, Humam has documented
OL,7,Fthe lives of thousands of people
OL,8,Fimpacted by the war, but now, he says,
OL,9,Fhe is looking to rebuild his own,
OL,10,Fhopeful for the future of his homeland
OL,11,Fand its people.
